00:55:41.340 --> 00:55:42.090
That's an outcome.

00:55:45.840 --> 00:55:50.200
So you could work this out,
so I won't go through it.

00:55:50.200 --> 00:55:53.400
You just push it
through the other side,

00:55:53.400 --> 00:55:56.260
and you can figure
