01:06:09.960 --> 01:06:18.450
So Lorentz covariance
requires us

01:06:18.450 --> 01:06:25.750
to take a trace to get a scalar,
and so we basically have trace.

01:06:25.750 --> 01:06:28.190
We can put anything
we like here.

01:06:28.190 --> 01:06:33.910
And then we have gamma Hv, which
