01:06:33.910 --> 01:06:36.613
the heavy quark part.

01:06:36.613 --> 01:06:38.530
So we just have to write
down the most general

01:06:38.530 --> 01:06:39.850
x that we can think of.

01:06:44.380 --> 01:06:47.260
And there's not
that much we can do

01:06:47.260 --> 01:06:50.690
because there's not that
