01:08:11.230 --> 01:08:14.190
So the way that you
should think about this

01:08:14.190 --> 01:08:22.855
is that in the matrix element
and only in the matrix element,

01:08:22.855 --> 01:08:25.140
but between these
ground-state mesons,

01:08:25.140 --> 01:08:32.310
I can really think that I've
made some connection that

01:08:32.310 --> 01:08:33.540
looks like as follows.

01:08:33.540 --> 01:08:38.279
That Q gamma H v--

01:08:38.279 --> 01:08:51.830
sorry, Qv is a over 2 times
this trace of gamma Hv

01:08:51.830 --> 01:08:54.680
if I'm in the matrix element.

01:08:54.680 --> 01:08:56.840
And then I know how to
take matrix elements

01:08:56.840 --> 01:08:58.215
with these fields
because they're

01:08:58.215 --> 01:09:00.840
the fields that actually are
annihilating those states.

01:09:00.840 --> 01:09:06.890
So then Q bar gamma
mu, gamma 5, capital

01:09:06.890 --> 01:09:14.330
Q. Now I'm using HQET states.

01:09:14.330 --> 01:09:17.537
They're actually
