01:09:17.537 --> 01:09:19.870
And I just use the formula
that I've derived over there.

01:09:34.189 --> 01:09:36.050
And I get these two results.

01:09:36.050 --> 01:09:39.705
So for HQET states, I
have only one constant, a.

01:09:39.705 --> 01:09:41.330
And that's because
heavy quark symmetry

01:09:41.330 --> 01:09:42.680
related the decay constants.

01:09:46.752 --> 01:09:48.210
And if I look at
all the dimensions

01:09:48.210 --> 01:09:51.149
